<li><a href="http://www.zoom.co.jp/english/products/h1/" target="_blank" class="liexternal">Zoom H1</a> AudioRecorder</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Software</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://audacity.sourceforge.net/" target="_blank" class="liexternal">Audacity</a> Aufnahme und Schnittprogramm</li>
<li>AT&amp;T Labs Natural Voices® <a href="http://www.research.att.com/projects/Natural_Voices/index.html" target="_blank" class="liexternal">Text-to-Speech</a></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Musik</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Freie Musik von der Musikplattform <a href="http://www.jamendo.com" target="_blank" class="liexternal">jamendo.com</a></li>
</ul>
